{"tid":1385926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"另類罷工模式","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:30:13.000Z","uid":35084,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f02768568e16b23cecc14269c23bfaf01a2c7ae6","tid":1385926,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"【職場熱話】日本車長「集改札罷工」 示範工業行動如何不擾民！<br />\n<br />\n最貼心的罷工<br />\n<br />\n員工要爭取他們認為是合理的待遇或要求是可以理解的，但要在進行工業行動時又不擾民，又可怎樣做？<br />\n<br />\n日本的岡山縣岡山市早前就有一種稱為「集改札罷工」的方法：一間名為「兩備巴士」的運輸公司，它的工會成員於去年曾有兩天用白布覆蓋巴士內的收費用投幣箱，布上還貼上「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不收車費</strong></span>」的告示。<br />\n<br />\n工會有如此舉動，皆因當地政府批准另一公司所設的循環小巴路線將與兩備巴士的部分服務路線重疊，而且對方的車資將會更便宜，因此工會成員憂心公司營收會受到影響，最終令工作不保，因此便發起罷工向公司抗議。<br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4/186215/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7-%E9%9B%86%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F186215%2F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%259C%25AD%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25AF%2584%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2593%25BE%25E6%25B0%2591&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI54W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=45ca48fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4/186215/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7-%E9%9B%86%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03d8M9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2